on-arrival: Prime Minister = "Empty"; prime_minister_party = "Labour"; labour_in_government = 1; in_labour_majority = 1; pro_republic += 5; foreign_minister_party = "Labour"; foreign_minister = "MacDonald"; home_secretary_party = "Labour"; home_secretary = "Henderson"; attorney_general_party = "Labour"; attorney_general = "Hastings"; labour_minister_party = "Labour"; labour_minister = "Shaw"; secretary_of_state_for_war_party = "Labour"; secretary_of_state_for_war_party = "Walsh"; health_minister_party = "Labour"; health_minister = "Wheatley"; chancellor_of_the_exchequer_party = "Labour"; chancellor_of_the_exchequer_party = "Snowden"; agriculture_minister_party = "Labour"; agriculture_minister = "Buxton"; reichswehr_loyalty -= 0.05; 
achievement: majority_party

Labour has won enough seats to govern alone! A historic victory. We now have the mandate to implement our agenda. anything is possible. 


- @macdonald_majority_chancellor: Ramsay MacDonald is Prime Minister.


In total, [+ no_confidence_votes +]% of the Reichstag is against us. [? if no_confidence_succeeds : We have lost the vote of no confidence. ?]

- @no_confidence_elections_new: There will be new elections, which we will try to delay.
- @no_confidence_win: We have won, for now.


@no_confidence_elections_new
on-arrival: {!
Q.in_emergency_government = 1;
Q.no_majority_elections += 1;
Q.next_election_month = Q.month + 6;
Q.next_election_time = Q.time + 6;
if (Q.next_election_month > 12) {
    Q.next_election_month -= 12;
    Q.next_election_year = Q.year + 1;
} else {
    Q.next_election_year = Q.year;
}
Q.pro_republic -= 5;
Q.workers_spd -= 3;
Q.new_middle_spd -= 3;
Q.old_middle_spd -= 3;
Q.rural_spd -= 3;
Q.catholics_spd -= 3;
Q.workers_nsdap += 5;
Q.old_middle_nsdap += 3;
Q.new_middle_nsdap += 3;
Q.rural_nsdap += 3;
Q.unemployed_nsdap += 5;
if (Q.pro_republic < 45 && Q.pro_republic >= 38) {
    Q.workers_spd -= 6;
}
if (Q.pro_republic < 38) {
    Q.workers_spd *= 0.85;
    Q.new_middle_spd -= 5;
    Q.old_middle_spd -= 5;
    Q.rural_spd -= 5;
    Q.catholics_spd -= 3;
    Q.workers_nsdap += 5;
    Q.old_middle_nsdap += 5;
    Q.new_middle_nsdap += 5;
    Q.rural_nsdap += 5;
    Q.unemployed_nsdap += 5;   
}
!}
view-if: no_confidence_votes > 50

The next elections are set for [+ next_election_month : month +] [+ next_election_year +].


@no_confidence_win
view-if: no_confidence_votes <= 50
on-arrival: in_minority_government = 1; in_emergency_government = 0;
achievement: minderheitsregierung

We have won the vote of no confidence, and are currently ruling under an SPD minority government. Now our task is to fix the country.


@weimar_coalition
title: We can form a Weimar Coalition.
subtitle: SPD + Z + [+ ddp_name +] [? if sapd_formed and cpgb_relation >= 30 : + SAPD toleration ?] ([+ weimar_coalition +]%)
